{"tid":1756984,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"區選選完重有黑社會呢個隱藏主線要搞","createTime":"2019-11-26T09:51:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T09:55:05.000Z","uid":69650,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"adabeb58d145de706a0ba41118bb2e1be4d04ea1","tid":1756984,"uid":69650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T09:51:22.000Z","msg":"搞唔好就腥風血雨,有冇人有自己區既黑社會野要講？<br />\n<br />\n講左元朗區先,10月中開始 <br />\n元朗d雞日頭做到夜晚勤力到仆街,d雞既密度無變都係一條街四五隻<br />\n但條條街都實有一隻半隻雞係到<br />\n天水圍區小販檔天未黑哂7點就開檔,早左唔小<br />\n<br />\n好多都係區議員默認左十幾廿年,依家係第一次大換血實搞到黑社會<br />\n見有風吹黑裝修,真心覺得唔好主動搞黑社會,睇怕黑社會黎緊會主動出擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c0e31b4e23a13c80bd4fd8f33da6c43fcf267b","tid":1756984,"uid":69761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T09:52:45.000Z","msg":"休息夠啦大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1161ab669b0b4d691007262b7e6e48c13142ad90","tid":1756984,"uid":69650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03c0e31b4e23a13c80bd4fd8f33da6c43fcf267b","tid":1756984,"uid":69761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T09:52:45.000Z","msg":"休息夠啦大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T09:55:05.000Z","msg":"手足出擊都要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}